'''Meerian''' was the native [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Meerian/Legends|Meerian]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Bandomeer/Legends|Bandomeer]]. Most Meerians were fluent in both Meerian and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language.

